        Group Snapshot object represents a point-in-time copy of a group of volumes.
        Parameters:
        groupSnapshotID - [required] Unique ID of the new group snapshot.
        groupSnapshotUUID - [required] UUID of the group snapshot.
        members - [required] List of volumeIDs and snapshotIDs for each member of the group.
        name - [required] Name of the group snapshot, or, if none was given, the UTC formatted day and time on which the snapshot was created.
        createTime - [required] The UTC formatted day and time on which the snapshot was created.
        status - [required] Status of the snapshot.
        attributes - [required] List of Name/Value pairs in JSON object format.
        Since:
        7.0
